            <note xml:id="foot.f7">T. H. Huxley and Etheridge 1865. See also <ref target="./DCP-LETT-2185.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">letter to T. H. Huxley, 16 December [1857]</ref>.</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f8">J. D. Hooker 1860. See <ref target="./DCP-LETT-2188.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">letter from J. D. Hooker, [17–23 December 1857]</ref> and n. 5.</note>
